{"tid":1701251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【當頭潑冷水】特朗普：沒有同意取消對中國加徵的關稅","createTime":"2019-11-09T02:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T03:15:28.000Z","uid":173631,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"56b40f9885f03240df3dc6be932ad227e06303c5","tid":1701251,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/finance/system/2019/11/09/010131176.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Ffinance%2Fsystem%2F2019%2F11%2F09%2F010131176.shtml&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=a713900f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/finance/system/2019/11/09/010131176.shtml</a>【橙訊】中美貿易談判再出現變數，傳中國希望美國取消貿易戰所加徵的關稅，然後才會購買多達500億美元農產品。美國總統特朗普表態，「我並沒有同意取消對中國的關稅」，他補充，那是中國希望撤回關稅，但他未有同意撤銷。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮向記者否認同意在中美首階段貿易協議，撤回向中國商品徵稅。他認為是中方希望撤銷部份關稅，而不是全面撤銷，因為北京知道他不會這樣做，中國亦比美國更希望達成協議，如果達成協議，將會在美國艾奧瓦州等國內地方簽署。<br />\n<br />\n白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅表示，華府願意推遲下月向中國貨加徵的關稅，一切由總統決定，但不是撤銷現有關稅，認為是很大分別。<br />\n<br />\n白宮首席經濟顧問庫德洛亦指，中美在首階段協議談判取得進展，若果最終簽署落實，將會包括取消關稅的協議及讓步。"},{"pid":"64376b130eb181ff32ca2798c31fbb28249ed280","tid":1701251,"uid":247300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:01:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"996148d0f7b59415a90a51bd4cde14b40d6a1a7d","tid":1701251,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:01:46.000Z","msg":"又彈出彈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444359f0239ad6e8696e5960cc52d015728a0638","tid":1701251,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:02:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6911cc8e916c9139f1a169be55a0def8da968f2d","tid":1701251,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"美國：未簽得成都唔撤關稅住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc3f72f54333ae7d7719aac84f86257aae52601","tid":1701251,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:03:41.000Z","msg":"橙仔報嘅，即係有紅媒認證。真係打到應一應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c8ef2855d91f284d8dc76c2cfe12c9cea81fb8","tid":1701251,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:04:23.000Z","msg":"Trump 2020 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aacc90948235de2bc94951590372a6e4594460c","tid":1701251,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:05:34.000Z","msg":"中美貿易談判再出現變數<br />\n呢句嘢出現過幾多次"},{"pid":"ea7bd4e08722d11e2f3b42a2635cb9d0d1f9002e","tid":1701251,"uid":46447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:06:18.000Z","msg":"曱甴平is my friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a9345d0df217a703ef4a909707fb44d944af4b","tid":1701251,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:08:29.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗諗都知係fake news<br />\n之前所有嘅所謂&quot;trump已跪&quot;新聞都係出自左派媒體<br />\n目的唔係為左報新聞,而係純粹為左抹黑"},{"pid":"4a9cd3159f46d8d486ab0e27fc6c321b395ea626","tid":1701251,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19a9345d0df217a703ef4a909707fb44d944af4b","tid":1701251,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:08:29.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗諗都知係fake news<br />\n之前所有嘅所謂&quot;trump已跪&quot;新聞都係出自左派媒體<br />\n目的唔係為左報新聞,而係純粹為左抹黑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:15:28.000Z","msg":"同造市"}]}